      "description": "Available is a 2011 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This E92 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example, boasting a 414 hp output with an 8,400 RPM redline. The engine retains its signature individual throttle body response, and preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service has been addressed. The chassis utilizes the factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque vectoring. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the carbon fiber roof is intact and the hydraulic steering rack provides exceptional feedback. Recent fluid analysis confirms the health of the high-strung valvetrain. A purist-spec machine optimized for performance longevity.",
